name: Nel / Nelliel Tu Odelschwanck (Bleach)

FINALLY!

I managed to create a nel TI that i'm happy with and that delivers consistently good results. This was trained on NAI with 4 different data sets on multiple different weights over 35,000 steps with over 400 images.
I know that by now there's an amazing LORA by Rakosz but i prefer TI's and really wanted to make it work.

This is a textual inversion embedding for Nelliel Tu Odelschwanck, or short Nel, from Bleach. Use vslinx_nel to activate.

Recommended is to use Clip Skip 2 since the embedding was trained on it!

Feedback is very welcomed and i'd love to see your creations with it if you'd like to attach them in a review.

The images were created with different models:

  • Corneo's 7th Heaven Mix

  • BloodNightOrangeMix
